{"tid":1678425,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【任務欄】你盡了責任沒有？這是你今天必須在Twitter/Reddit/FB廣傳的警暴資料","createTime":"2019-10-27T16:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T18:30:29.000Z","uid":54684,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b14e8954dbb8cfe6999eac01c12f9a0dd80c5d3f","tid":1678425,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"(1) 警方主動挑動了和平集會的民眾，破壞和平集會，令人民再一次被迫進衝突了<br />\nOn 2019-10-27 (Sun), police intimidated peaceful assembly near Tsim Sha Tsui, assaulted them with pepper spray and stirred up troubles with peaceful citizens again, forcing people's peaceful assembly into clashes with the police. <br />\n(入Link有片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HeungGongJai/status/1188368584252116994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHeungGongJai%2Fstatus%2F1188368584252116994&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=187e8f07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHeungGongJai%2Fstatus%2F1188368584252116994&h=f432e09e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HeungGongJai/status/1188368584252116994</a><br />\n<br />\n(2) 警方用槍指著在海旁和平集會控訴警方暴行的市民，隨時準備扣下扳機。<br />\nPolice gathered at high position and used guns to point at peaceful assembly at the waterfront which protested against police brutality during the 4-month long protests, ready to open fire at any time. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpw7mPm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frpw7mPm.jpg&h=a86df28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1188412763237830658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1188412763237830658&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=d2ab25cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1188412763237830658&h=58bb8fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1188412763237830658</a><br />\n<br />\n(3) 多名防暴警不斷追打1名男青年，其間拉扯該男子的背心，並以手上的警棍、甚或胡椒噴劑鐵罐，打向該男子的頭部和身體。<br />\nPolice officers chased a boy and hit his head and body with batons and metal cans. This further angered the citizens around. <br />\n(入Link有片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191027/60201390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60201390&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=bfce3d47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60201390&h=efc58744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191027/60201390</a><br />\n<br />\n(4) <br />\n本台攝影師晚上在旺角彌敦道採訪期間，被防暴警察阻撓及推撞，並強行脫下面罩，警方在現場曾多次施放催淚彈。本台攝影師當時戴著記者證，並身穿印有港台標誌的反光衣，攝影機亦貼上港台標誌。<br />\n<br />\n本台攝影師當時在行人路上拍攝，一名持長槍的防暴警員突然走向他，推他的肩膀，強行扯下他的面罩，又推開攝影機。<br />\n<br />\n十多名防暴警員到場分隔開該名警員及圍觀人士，又手持盾牌及警棍，要求在場其他記者及市民走開。有警員向一名外籍人士問「你CIA呀? 」，外籍人士之後離開。<br />\n<br />\nPolice officers assaulted a news reporter, stopped them from reporting, forcibly removed his face mask after they released rounds of tear gas at the scene and pushed away his camera. The news reporter showed his reporter pass and had a clear logo of the news agency (RTHK, the local government-funded news agency) on his vest and his camera. <br />\n<br />\nOther police officers later arrived and challenged a foreigner nearby as a CIA agent by saying &quot;Are you CIA?&quot;. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1488492_2_20191027224327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1488492_2_20191027224327.jpg&h=aa468508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(入Link有片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488492-20191027.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488492-20191027.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=31b0b700\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488492-20191027.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=86bd77c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488492-20191027.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(5) 外國攝影記者被捕<br />\nPhotographer May James, who mostly freelances for HKFP, has been arrested in Mong Kok whilst at work. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oosVvGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoosVvGU.jpg&h=39c9a2bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1188469817495322625?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftomgrundy%2Fstatus%2F1188469817495322625%3Fs%3D21&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=e713525d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftomgrundy%2Fstatus%2F1188469817495322625%3Fs%3D21&h=1de9c29d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1188469817495322625?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(6) 有市民目睹警察懷疑動用私刑毆打被捕人士<br />\n2218 #旺角 #通菜街 #女人街<br />\n地上有大量血跡，有市民目睹警察懷疑動用私刑毆打被捕人士，但被警察推走並以強光照射，故無法拍攝當時情況。<br />\n#蘋果<br />\nPolice was witnessed using extrajudicial violence against arrested persons near Mong Kok. The witness was pushed away and flashed at by stong light by the police, and he failed to film the incident. The site was tainted by massive blood. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oM7FGmU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoM7FGmU.jpg&h=e796f57d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75300883bb97fe7f94afb341965d6568b538c496","tid":1678425,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"請將今日的警暴情況/記者中槍的tweet