like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=3cea7273\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=a8028e0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=37ab1a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"b728c3f7ad17d39bf18e52a0b8e49412f668f811","tid":1678425,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"886c0a21dcf40982182eb8e634200c1116de8051","tid":1678425,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"有咩hashtag要用"},{"pid":"7598f8fec0dfc90db7fcc2821cd97388044de1b7","tid":1678425,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"(8) 【10.27 1745 述德街，太子道西交界】制服左都要補多腳？<br />\nPolice officers viciously kicked an arrested man who was already laying on the ground and facing down. <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2659682630755585/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflyingshadows%2Fvideos%2F2659682630755585%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4UlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=1e2e1d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2659682630755585/</a>"},{"pid":"683b230819140e13b8acb6ba6d99828e63a920de","tid":1678425,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hG1OQOu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhG1OQOu.gif&h=3a671a6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41f1961cd0126943f893e3383f899dda07ebb229","tid":1678425,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:18: